<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - (ly ạlḥyạẗ hy ạlmsyḥ wạlmwt ly rbḥ yryḥ)2
 1- (hw ạlly ạftdạny mn ạlmwt ạlrhyb hw ạlly ạ̹sẖtrạny bạldm ʿly ạlṣlyb)2
 2- (hw ạlly rậny wạ̉nạ fy ạ̉rḍ ạlʿbyd hw ạlly fy ṣlybh ạ̉nạ ḥr wsʿyd)2
 3- (hw ạlly ʿlạny wạ̉nạ ʿbd wḥqyr jh wkẖd mkạny wạ̉nạ nlt ạltbryr )2
 4- (hw ạlly byrʿạny wạ̉nạ fy ạ̉rḍ ạlṣʿạb wḍạmn mkạny hnạk fy byt ạlậb)2</lyrics>
